gov.va.med.srcalc.web.view.admin

Class EditExistingRule

  • java.lang.Object
    • gov.va.med.srcalc.web.view.admin.EditRule
      • gov.va.med.srcalc.web.view.admin.EditExistingRule

  • public class EditExistingRule
extends EditRule

    An interface for editing an existing Rule.

    The high-level workflow is:

    1. Construct an instance based on an existing rule.
    2. Present the user with the current values and allow her to update the properties as desired.
    3. Use the EditRuleValidator validator to validate the user's edits.
    4. Call #applyToRule() to update the target rule with the new properties.
